data.description:
Charming 3 story home featuring 5 BR, 2 BA, large eat-in kitchen with new stove and refrigerator 2018, main
floor laundry and a heated front porch for year round enjoyment. There are wood floors throughout the main level, including the main floor bedroom. Beautiful oak woodwork and unique old craftsman features such as built-ins with leaded glass doors and columns between living/dining rooms. This home has 3 bedrooms on the second level and also a full bath; the third level is one large bedroom with built-in storage under the eaves. The basement is unfinished but does have a large room to the back that could be a great family/game room. Outside you will find an oversized 2 stall garage with parking and plug-in for an RV, fenced in backyard, stone patio and a lovely landscaped yard.  You won’t want to miss this one!
